<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0-beta/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-/Y6pD6FV/Vv2HJnA6t+vslU6fwYXjCFtcEpHbNJ0lyAFsXTsjBbfaDjzALeQsN6M" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <title>Bootstrap Sandbox</title>
</head>
<body>
    {{> header}}

      <div class="container">
        <!--####################START HERE#####################-->

          <legend class="text-center text-md-left">Agendamentos registrados</legend>
          <small class="form-text text-muted text-center text-md-left mb-2">Todos os agendamentos criados no sistema são apresentados abaixo.</small>

          <ul class="list-group mb-2 my-3">
            {{#each schedules}}
              <a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action text-center text-md-left" href="/schedule/{{this.name}}">{{this.name}}</a>
            {{/each}}
          </ul>

        <legend class="text-center text-md-left mt-3">Criando novos agendamentos</legend>
        <p class="lead text-justify">Você não pode alterar os dados de um agendamento já existente! Porém, você pode excluí-los e criar novos como desejar. Para tal, selecione a opção de criar novos agendamento a direita!</p>

        <a href="/newSchedule">
          <button type="submit" class=" my-4 btn btn-primary btn-block">Criar novo agendamento!</button>
        </a>

    </div><!-- ./container -->

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.2.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-KJ3o2DKtIkvYIK3UENzmM7KCkRr/rE9/Qpg6aAZGJwFDMVNA/GpGFF93hXpG5KkN" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.11.0/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-b/U6ypiBEHpOf/4+1nzFpr53nxSS+GLCkfwBdFNTxtclqqenISfwAzpKaMNFNmj4" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0-beta/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-h0AbiXch4ZDo7tp9hKZ4TsHbi047NrKGLO3SEJAg45jXxnGIfYzk4Si90RDIqNm1" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>
